---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import StructuredData from '../../components/StructuredData.astro';
import { getAffiliateCTA } from '../../config/affiliate-links';
---

<Layout title="AI Website Builders Under $10/Month (2025): Budget Options">
  <StructuredData type="WebPage" data={{ name: 'AI Website Builders Under $10/Month', description: 'Budget AI website builders compared. Hostinger is cheapest at $2.99. Free tiers vs paid. When to spend more vs stay cheap.', url: 'https://aiwebsitebuilders.com/categories/ai-website-builders-under-10' }} />

  <section class="bg-[#FFF8F0] py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">AI Builders Under $10:<span class="block text-[#F5521A]">Budget Options</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mt-6">Cheapest AI builders compared. Free tiers, budget options, value analysis.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Quick Answer</h2>
      <div class="bg-orange-50 border-[3px] border-orange-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">üí∞ Cheapest with Features: Hostinger at $2.99/month</p>
        <p class="text-sm mb-4">Includes hosting, decent templates, AI generation.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-orange-600"><strong>Reality:</strong> Most "under $10" options are limited. Consider spending $15-20 for significantly better tools.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Under $10 Options</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Hostinger</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">$2.99/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Cheapest AI Builder</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">Includes hosting, domain (first year), decent templates, AI generation. Best for absolute lowest cost.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">AI features are basic. Support can be slow. Limited templates.</div>
          {getAffiliateCTA('hostinger')}
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">WordPress + Elementor AI</h3>
            <span class="bg-[#F5521A] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm">$5-9/mo</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Self-Hosted Budget Option</p>
          <p class="text-sm mb-4">Hosting ($5-9/mo) + WordPress (free) + Elementor AI plugin. Requires tech skills. Unlimited potential.</p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-600 mb-4">Manual setup. Security/updates on you. Steep learning curve.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Free Tiers (Technically $0)</h2>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-[3px] border-green-400 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-3">üÜì Free Options Exist</p>
        <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Relume AI:</strong> Free forever. Planning/sitemaps only, not hosting.</li>
          <li><strong>Wix Free:</strong> Unlimited pages, 500MB storage. Wix branding, no custom domain.</li>
          <li><strong>Framer Free:</strong> 2 pages, 1GB storage. Framer branding, no custom domain.</li>
          <li><strong>Durable Free:</strong> 3 pages, limited features. Durable branding.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-xs text-green-600 mt-4">All free tiers have catches: builder branding, no custom domain, feature limits. Good for testing only.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Budget vs Value Analysis</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">‚úì Choose Under $10 If...</p>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ You genuinely can't afford $15/month</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ This is a hobby project, not business-critical</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You just need something basic online</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You're comfortable with technical setup (WordPress option)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2">‚ö†Ô∏è Spend $15-20 If...</p>
          <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ This is for a business that makes money</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You need better AI generation quality</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You want more templates and better design</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You care about professional results</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ You want better support and features</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">The Value Math</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 text-white">
        <p class="text-base mb-4">Saving $12/month = <strong class="text-[#F5521A]">$144/year</strong></p>
        <p class="text-base mb-4">For a business website: <strong class="text-[#F5521A]">Not worth it.</strong> The difference in quality, AI capability, and features is worth far more than $144/year.</p>
        <p class="text-base mb-4">For a personal project: <strong class="text-[#F5521A]">Maybe.</strong> If budget is tight, start cheap and upgrade later.</p>
        <p class="text-base"><strong class="text-[#F5521A]">Recommendation:</strong> If this site makes money (or will), spend the extra $12/month. You'll earn it back quickly with better results.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6">Price Comparison Table</h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-xl border-[3px] border-gray-200">
          <thead class="bg-gray-900 text-white">
            <tr><th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-bold">Builder</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Price</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Pages</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">Custom Domain</th><th class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold">AI Quality</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Hostinger</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$2.99/mo</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">100</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">‚úì</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Basic</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">WordPress + Elementor</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$5-9/mo</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Unlimited</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">‚úì</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Good</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Relume AI (Free)</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$0</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Unlimited</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">N/A*</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Excellent</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Wix Free</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$0</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Unlimited</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-red-600">‚úó</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center text-yellow-600">Basic</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Framer Free</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">$0</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center">2</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-red-600">‚úó</td><td class="px-4 py-3 text-center font-bold text-green-600">Excellent</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2">* Relume is planning/wireframing, not hosting. Export code to host elsewhere.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
